1
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:21,570
Why is Du Yu watching us?

2
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:23,640
What is his goal?

3
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:27,400
Actually,

4
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:29,440
I don't know his goal either.

5
00:01:30,039 --> 00:01:31,240
He just told me

6
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:33,479
that if you make any move,

7
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,960
I must report it to him.

8
00:01:36,320 --> 00:01:37,360
He actually

9
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:39,570
wants to drive a wedge between you.

10
00:01:42,039 --> 00:01:44,370
Then what is your relationship with Du Yu?

11
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:47,479
Years ago,

12
00:01:48,039 --> 00:01:50,880
my family had a marriage contract with the Du family's eldest son.

13
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:52,039
But for some reason,

14
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,160
three years ago,

15
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:55,100
the Du family's eldest son

16
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:56,840
fell ill and died.

17
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:58,400
At that time,

18
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:00,640
my family was still quite prominent.

19
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:03,170
Du Zong didn't want to give up on the marriage.

20
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,360
So he brought Du Yu to propose.

21
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:04,760
Uncle,

22
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:06,820
I hope the engagement stands.

23
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,720
But my feelings for Miss Chuyun

24
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:09,440
are real.

25
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:11,120
I hope

26
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,720
you can give me a chance, Uncle.

27
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,440
A chance?

28
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:17,560
What right do you have to ask for a chance?

29
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:25,760
You want a chance?

30
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:26,400
Fine.

31
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,440
Let me see

32
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:35,480
what qualifies you to be my son-in-law.

33
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,720
Miss,

34
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:38,600
don't go out.

35
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:40,560
Uncle.

36
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:43,960
This wine represents my feelings for Miss Chuyun.

37
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,600
I am a concubine's son,

38
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:46,800
but

39
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:49,800
my love for her is witnessed by heaven and earth.

40
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,680
Please grant my wish, Uncle.

41
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:00,560
Miss.

42
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:06,280
Unless you are willing to be a live-in son-in-law.

43
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:09,040
Otherwise, how could I let my precious daughter

44
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:10,900
marry a concubine's son like you?

45
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:14,200
Uncle, becoming a live-in son-in-law

46
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,860
is something I cannot accept.

47
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:17,570
I will prove with my actions

48
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,700
that I can make Miss Chuyun

49
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:20,840
happy.

50
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:21,520
Tch.

51
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:24,000
No talent, yet so much pride.

52
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,640
Duzong,

53
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,640
look at your son.

54
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:29,480
It's humiliating.

55
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:30,760
I think

56
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:31,800
this marriage

57
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:33,800
should be called off.

58
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:34,520
No, no, no.

59
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,640
Master Chu,

60
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,200
please calm down first.

61
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:38,600
Duyu is still young after all.

62
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:40,000
He doesn't understand many things.

63
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:40,760
When I go back,

64
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:41,960
I will teach him well.

65
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:42,960
But look,

66
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:43,960
about this marriage,

67
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:44,800
can't we

68
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,400
discuss it further?

69
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,480
You all saw it.

70
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,440
It's not that our Chu family is heartless.

71
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:53,680
It's just that Duyu

72
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:55,920
is not good enough for my daughter.

73
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:59,200
Our Chu family cares about our reputation.

74
00:03:59,240 --> 00:03:59,640
Today,

75
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:01,960
this concubine's son came to propose,

76
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,840
insulting our family.

77
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:04,700
From now on,

78
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:07,440
the rent for your clinic will increase by fifty percent

79
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:08,520
as compensation.

80
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,240
Fifty percent?

81
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,560
You absolutely cannot do that,

82
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,200
Master Chu.

83
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:13,120
Our clinic is a small business.

84
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,960
We really can't afford it.

85
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,160
You concubine's son!

86
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,079
Useless thing!

87
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:23,140
Hurry up and apologize to Master Chu!

88
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:23,920
Father,

89
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:25,560
I didn't do anything wrong.

90
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:25,960
You...

91
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,400
You bastard!

92
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,600
A concubine's son is just a concubine's son.

93
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,200
Do you want to get our whole family killed?

94
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:33,440
Apologize now!

95
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,040
Master Chu,

96
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,600
I overestimated myself

97
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,760
and was presumptuous.

98
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,490
Please forgive me, Master Chu.

99
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:44,240
Enough.

100
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:46,090
I'll let you off the hook today.

101
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:47,860
Remember this.

102
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:49,920
The Du family

103
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:51,600
will have no further ties

104
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:54,440
with my family.

105
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,040
Yes.

106
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:57,920
Master Chu,

107
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:59,440
we will take our leave.

108
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:00,760
Back then,

109
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,920
even though I had

110
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,650
no romantic feelings for Du Yu,

111
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:07,360
seeing him humiliated for my sake

112
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,920
still touched my heart.

113
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:12,180
Thinking of everything he did...

114
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:15,040
It was all just to maintain the family's interests and face.

115
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,520
How tragic.

116
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:21,520
Perhaps that is why,

117
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:25,200
when my father went up the mountain to pay respects, Duyu...

118
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,400
Brutally killed him?

119
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:28,490
And wiped out my entire family.

120
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:30,840
The reason I survived

121
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:34,240
was because I accidentally fell off a cliff.

122
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,880
Although I survived,

123
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:38,120
I lost my sight because of it.

124
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,600
Duyu is so cruel.

125
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,520
When he first found me,

126
00:05:46,960 --> 00:05:48,520
he intended to kill me.

127
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:51,200
But seeing that I was already blind,

128
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:54,200
he pretended to be my savior.

129
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:58,159
And used me as a vessel to cultivate poisonous insects.

130
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,760
How did you discover the truth?

131
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:05,640
I saw the killer's face back then,

132
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:08,000
but I didn't know it was Duyu.

133
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,900
After I regained my sight,

134
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:13,240
I saw his face

135
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:16,220
and recognized him immediately.

136
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:19,480
Later, when he killed Duzong,

137
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,020
I was there too.

138
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,900
Although I couldn't move freely,

139
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,600
I heard every word

140
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,840
they said clearly.

141
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,340
His father?

142
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:32,360
He killed Duzong too?

143
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:34,600
Yes. Not only Duzong,

144
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,000
but Old Hu

145
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:38,760
and Hu the Second also fell victim to him.

146
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:41,480
He exploited Hu the Second's greed,

147
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:43,740
making the brothers kill each other.

148
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,520
To become test subjects

149
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:48,570
for his new poisonous insects.

150
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,360
I don't know

151
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:56,200
how I could have loved such a man before.

152
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:09,640
Are you okay?

153
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,160
What's wrong?

154
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:12,440
Are you all right?

155
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:14,440
It's Duyu.

156
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:16,600
It's Duyu.

157
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:20,040
If...

158
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:22,400
I really lose control,

159
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,600
you must...

160
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:26,770
What are you talking about?

161
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,880
I will save you.

162
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,440
I know my own body.

163
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,800
Before I lose my mind,

164
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:39,400
You all,

165
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,800
stay away from me.

166
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:43,520
I won't give up on you.

167
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,480
Whatever happens,

168
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,810
we'll face it together.

169
00:07:46,159 --> 00:07:46,720
Doctor Ji.

170
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:48,360
I'll distract Duyu for you.

171
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:50,440
Be careful.

172
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:01,840
Xiao Heyan.

173
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,480
Ji Bai.

174
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,540
Use the scalpel

175
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,280
to remove the poisonous insect.

176
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:18,080
No.

177
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:19,960
I can't do it.

178
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,480
Ji Bai, you can do it.

179
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,480
I know you have a way.

180
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:29,600
The poisonous insect is inside your chest.

181
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:31,200
It's too close to your heart.

182
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,400
I'm afraid.

183
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:34,799
I'm afraid it will be just like your mother.

184
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:48,080
Ji Bai, look at me.

185
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:51,640
You're not that child anymore.

186
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:53,880
I trust you.

187
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:55,820
Whatever the outcome,

188
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,640
we'll face it together.

189
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,560
Do it.

190
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:24,960
They couldn't have gone far.

191
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,200
Search thoroughly.

192
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:27,440
They must be hiding

193
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:29,120
in these woods.

194
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,160
Yes, Master Yan.

195
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:31,280
We've split up.

196
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:33,560
We'll notify you as soon as we find them.

197
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:34,920
Master Yan,

198
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:36,960
I'll take some men to check over there.

199
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:37,760
Go ahead.

200
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:46,600
Ji Bai.

201
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:47,840
Xiao Heyan.

202
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:50,800
You can't escape me.

203
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:53,480
Chuyun.

204
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:55,400
Why are you here?

205
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:57,360
I know everything.

206
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,960
I came here only to die.

207
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,880
Only if I die,

208
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:04,050
will the poisonous insect perish,

209
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:07,010
and you won't be able to use me to hurt anyone else.

210
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:07,640
Chuyun,

211
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,570
why do you think of me like that?

212
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:11,600
In fact,

213
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,680
you have always been in my heart.

214
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,400
I killed your father

215
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:17,800
because he looked down on my status

216
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:19,480
and tried to keep us apart.

217
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,000
I wronged you,

218
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:23,560
but I cannot lose you.

219
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:27,010
Don't do anything foolish.

220
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:28,400
Come to me.

221
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,540
I will make it up to you.

222
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:35,400
I know.

223
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:37,130
You're just lying to me.

224
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:39,800
You just want to use me to breed poisonous insects

225
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:41,600
to curry favor with Yan Quezuo.

226
00:10:42,520 --> 00:10:44,840
Why would I use you to please Yan Quezuo?

227
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:47,600
He's already poisoned.

228
00:10:48,040 --> 00:10:49,640
There were just too many people earlier,

229
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:51,100
so I couldn't make my move.

230
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:54,960
Chuyun.

231
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,250
Don't worry.

232
00:10:57,800 --> 00:10:58,920
In a little while,

233
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,520
Yan Quezuo will become my puppet.

234
00:11:02,560 --> 00:11:03,480
Then you and I

235
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:05,520
can truly be together.

236
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:09,440
Chuyun,

237
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:10,720
I know

238
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:13,280
you've always liked me.

239
00:11:14,760 --> 00:11:15,840
Can you forgive me?

240
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,920
Help me find Ji Bai and Xiao Heyan first,

241
00:11:28,920 --> 00:11:31,120
and then we'll deal with Yan Quezuo.

242
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:33,960
Then everything will be ours.

243
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,680
No one can ever separate us.

244
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:38,760
Okay.

245
00:11:39,160 --> 00:11:40,480
I'll take you to them.

246
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,080
Yi Yinan.

247
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:20,240
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

248
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:19,640
Xiaoxiaoxue, Yi Yinan.

249
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:20,840
Xiaoxiaoxue, Yi Yinan.

250
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:21,640
Xiaoxiaoxue.

251
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:49,640
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

252
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:53,720
Zhang.

253
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,240
Pan Xiulong.

254
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,080
Lu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.

255
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:54,680
Pan Xiulong.

256
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:54,480
Lu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.

257
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:54,800
Lu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.

258
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:54,800
Pan.
